name: Catjinni Demo
summary:
Survive. Customize. Conquer!  

Dive into a unique, Survivors-Like Action Game featuring RPG and rogue-lite elements. In Catjinni, you'll battle endless waves of monsters and face the Jinn Ifrit, who seeks to plunge the world into darkness with his malevolent ghouls. But fear not — your loyal companion Catjinni is by your side to claw through the shadow realm!  

Survive 7 Days and Nights  

Endure intense survival battles against increasingly powerful foes. Collect gold, upgrade your gear, and complete...
